    "lyrics": {
      "text": "Al le-lu---i-a, al-le--lu----i----a, a----le--lu-----i----a. \n\nO_ God Who giv-est a-venge-ment un-to me and hast sub-dued___ peo--ples___ un--der___ me.\n\nAl le-lu---i-a, al-le--lu----i----a, a----le--lu-----i----a. \n\nIt is He that mag-ni-fi-eth the sal-va-tion of His king and work-eth mer-cy for His a-noint-ed, for Da--vid, and for his seed__ un-to__ e---ter--ni---ty.\n\nAl le-lu---i-a, al-le--lu----i----a, a----le--lu-----i----a.____"
    }
